OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1779563472
OL,3,CArsenal win Premier League for first
OL,4,Ctime in 22 years
OL,6,FArsenal are Premier League champions
OL,7,Ffor the first time in 22 years after
OL,8,Fsecond-placed Manchester City were
OL,9,Fheld to a 1-1 draw by a Bournemouth
OL,10,Fside bound for Europe.
OL,12,FAmid reports manager Pep Guardiola
OL,13,Fwill step down at the end of the
OL,14,Fseason, City needed to win at Vitality
OL,15,FStadium to take the title race to the
OL,16,Ffinal day.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/4
