PN,40902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1779563472
OL,3,CArsenal win Premier League for first
OL,4,Ctime in 22 years
OL,6,FErling Haaland equalised in added time
OL,7,Fto cancel out Junior Kroupi's record-
OL,8,Fbreaking 13th top-flight goal of the
OL,9,Fcampaign but the visitors were unable
OL,10,Fto force a winner as Guardiola was
OL,11,Fdenied a potential fairytale farewell.
OL,13,FBournemouth's historic achievement was
OL,14,Fa fitting way to mark the final home
OL,15,Fgame of head coach Andoni Iraola, who
OL,16,Fwas given a rousing send-off at full-
OL,17,Ftime ahead of being replaced by Marco
OL,18,FRose in the summer.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/4
