PN,40903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1779563472
OL,3,CArsenal win Premier League for first
OL,4,Ctime in 22 years
OL,6,FFollowing a remarkable 17th league
OL,7,Fgame without loss, the Cherries are
OL,8,Fguaranteed a top-seven finish and
OL,9,Fremain in contention for Champions
OL,10,FLeague football ahead of Sunday's
OL,11,Fseason finale at Nottingham Forest.
OL,13,FCity are now an insurmountable four
OL,14,Fpoints adrift of the table-topping
OL,15,FGunners, with speculation Guardiola is
OL,16,Fset to end his contract a year early
OL,17,Fand be succeeded by Enzo Maresca after
OL,18,Fthe weekend visit of Aston Villa.
